Michael Adrian STONEBREAKER, Appellant/Petitioner(s),
v.
Kevin J. RAMBOSK, Sheriff, Appellee/Respondent(s). CASE NO.: 2D18-5098 District Court of Appeal of Florida, Second District. January 04, 2019

BY ORDER OF THE COURT:
